title: CROPPED BOMBER JACKET WITH SEQUIN EMBROIDERY
desc: Cropped bomber jacket in cotton- and silk-blend fabric. The item, presented at the Spring-Summer 25 Runway Show, is covered in shiny embroidered sequins and features an exquisite, contrasting and placed fil coupé jacquard floral motif with stencil-like effect.• Cropped fit• Shirt collar• Two-way zip closure• Made in Italy• The model is 5' 9½" (177 cm) tall and wears a size 40
